decks.notes: The main idea of this deck is to quickly cast spells, generate mana, and storm off to overwhelm the opponent with a flurry of powerful spells. Ral, Monsoon Mage acts as the commander, providing card advantage and extra spell damage. The deck includes a mix of cantrips, rituals, and powerful win conditions like Grapeshot and Bonus Round. Cards like Baral, Chief of Compliance and Goblin Electromancer help to reduce the cost of spells, while cards like Past in Flames and Mizzix's Mastery allow you to recycle your spells and keep the storm going. The goal is to efficiently chain together spells, generate a large storm count, and finish off the opponent in a single explosive turn.
